Name: texlive-mfpic4ode
License: LPPL
Summary: Macros to draw direction fields and solutions of ODEs
Version: %{tl_version}
Release: %{tl_noarch_release}.0.4.svn17745%{?dist}
BuildArch: noarch
Requires: texlive-base = %{tl_version}
